{"tid":1412040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"分化警察第一波--無啖好食","createTime":"2019-08-05T05:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T05:49:57.000Z","uid":296674,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e626a0f84a2a7de7989e5923d3ff56b6bdc65997","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:14:35.000Z","msg":"我喺外國睇完777行長記招之後嬲爆<br />\n今日同阿媽通長途電話之後有啲idea<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不如搞警察遊樂會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 地理：<span style=\"color: pink;\">位處太子，石硤尾，九龍塘之間</span></span><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/Police+Sports+and+Recreation+Club/@22.3301899,114.172372,16.12z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x340400ca45cd8091:0xdb2eb66ef5240087!8m2!3d22.3274154!4d114.1686583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2FPolice%2BSports%2Band%2BRecreation%2BClub%2F%4022.3301899%2C114.172372%2C16.12z%2Fdata%3D%214m5%213m4%211s0x340400ca45cd8091%3A0xdb2eb66ef5240087%218m2%213d22.3274154%214d114.1686583&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=1c148399\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/place/Police+Sports+and+Recreation+Club/@22.3301899,114.172372,16.12z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x340400ca45cd8091:0xdb2eb66ef5240087!8m2!3d22.3274154!4d114.1686583</a>，四通八達，暢通無阻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkAv24m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkAv24m.png&h=eb987861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">有事可以走去</span><br />\na. 彌敦道<br />\nb. 經<span style=\"font-size: large;\">陸軍球場</span>去石硤尾公屋區（大坑東西，南山邨係深水埗區民主派票倉，民主派得票率曾高達67%；據聞區選特登改劃界係為咗拆散佢哋）<br />\nc. 經<span style=\"font-size: large;\">花墟公園，陸軍球場</span>再上斜路去又一村／又一城（請自己衡量體力）<br />\nd. 經<span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角大球場</span>入九龍城，旺角東<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 目標</span><br />\na. 講到明係起比警察嘅，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就一定唔會搞到其他受尊敬嘅紀律部隊</span>。<br />\nb. 仲有，佢係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">員佐級警員唯一可以使用嘅遊樂設施（警官係灣仔有自己嘅club），可以令到所有藍衫黑警同埋老婆細佬冇地方好去</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 策略</span><br />\na. 大家諗下，如果黑警係自己唯一嘅clubhouse出面放蛋，速龍防暴辱罵或者打中休班嘅自己人或者家屬，一定會比自己友鬧爆，仲要拆埋自己招牌；呢個亦都係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">全力套取警員編號，崗位，樣貌特徵嘅好時機</span>。<br />\nb. 分化：呀sir有私人地方去，班藍衫無地方發洩（警察遊樂會有高規格體育設施，茶樓等），<span style=\"font-size: large;\">會妒忌上級</span>，呢個時候就可以出<span style=\"font-size: large;\">「白衫歎冷氣，藍衫去受死」</span>嘅口號啦<br />\nc. 要佢地老婆仔女去到邊都見到我提嘅文宣，尤其係天水圍女仔，無數路人被扑，黃大仙等等，令佢哋質疑自己人生嘅意義（<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 騎呢位</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係人哋地頭，人哋就更加熟路，</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Msm9Kx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Msm9Kx.png&h=350d21a7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n遊樂會一邊係界限街，一邊係好多酒吧嘅掘頭路（有山路可走），<br />\n附近有<span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角警署，有重兵</span>，<br />\n同休班警埋身肉搏未必贏，雖然肯定佢哋一定冇gear<br />\n各位一定要be water<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">講咁多，都係要打持久戰，輿論戰，分化戰<br />\n我呢個冷氣軍師冇得落場，就要同佢哋鬥智<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n一齊上 一齊落<br />\n香港人加油</span>"},{"pid":"d7454744d7c814453f8ea88985119e9fae46aa9d","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:20:17.000Z","msg":"更正：灣仔警官會所因為沙中線拆卸重建中<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AE%98%E6%9C%83%E6%89%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2589%2580&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWADrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=866170f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AD%A6%E5%AE%98%E6%9C%83%E6%89%80</a>"},{"pid":"6569adc77b3c4fed45de8c067dc5e516a0aa23b1","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:22:04.000Z","msg":"仲有，可以去買深水埗食清真菜添，長沙灣道好多嘢食架"},{"pid":"dfb8964fa3a495b9db78e00379227b7e88068cd8","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:24:33.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4f428cf32b398aba71be38fff5414050af950d31","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:25:31.000Z","msg":"對唔住我P牌，因為之前研究緊點樣用外國電郵註冊，終於比我攪掂"},{"pid":"ccafaabf7e481f43177d0eb446b2dec57917a14d","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:26:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"81cea40e6d7a4b245476e5bce50c8c1f805daa9b","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"仲有，罷工嘅各位除咗去集會之外，更加要用空餘時間諗<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日後嘅策略</span>，辛苦晒"},{"pid":"7993194fe49dce7cd16c4be703f34f833bd8ec8d","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:28:34.000Z","msg":"鬥智又鬥力，咁先至無敵"},{"pid":"aac54d6b368b19b16cb08bec5cb6b0d8a7149903","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:28:48.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"8b78909b16c52d2c7c5feed33150da90f6caafb8","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"我叫777做行長 係因為尼個係所有小學入面最被人恥笑嘅點<br />\n呢個<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行</span></strong>政<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長</span></strong>官考唔到第一就喊，我要連班小學生都笑死佢"},{"pid":"9f30041af08a89de75132884c8ac086be55b9fe2","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:35:19.000Z","msg":"有意見嘅同我講，我都係用有限嘅網絡睇live同埋立場新聞，連登<br />\n跟車唔貼請見諒啊"},{"pid":"63e9ac3d5e62252ef2a8812ea248cb7ed8731086","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:39:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"15cff773683c64afd9f5b80426ab0080567a1d3f","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:40:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1327b5cb79f6aab2ce8f8f49f53d2ec6a47a74c8","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:40:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"49ab180a598a6fdebde90dc0f93118b3d8776851","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"再再自推"},{"pid":"b1db65c7f7589fb6d9d1a8dfba1a2ca05aa0706d","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"再再再自推"},{"pid":"0a2f9ae09366f7dcc964f9a15c8be990213d2f02","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cbb2073a549275076e085d61d4b074cf7a923473","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"P牌都可以為香港出力"},{"pid":"25a2fa0c2a48f669a63a1da5798b80d4a2fb1dd7","tid":1412040,"uid":296674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T05:49:57.000Z","msg":"有冇人想去睇波踢波"}]}